sources.description:
One Veteran Against The Darkness | Monsters Within | 2025 Drama War Movie - Life brings Luke, a veteran, back to his hometown to see his sister, who has special needs. His arrival brings self reflection to face his monsters, and a chance meeting with Lily leads him to fight for something other than himself.

2025.  Stars: Devin Montgomery, Kendall Cavener, Skeeta Jenkins
